{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_3","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '241,520p' __issue_context__.json\"","aggregated_output":"      \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25399618844)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-05T20:09:58Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31882#issuecomment-4382638709\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABBTs5SQ\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"Done. Both terms have been obsoleted and replaced by `GO:1905349 ciliary transition zone assembly` per the consensus in this thread.\\n\\n- **GO:1905353** ciliary transition fiber assembly → `replaced_by: GO:1905349`\\n- **GO:0097711** ciliary basal body-plasma membrane docking → `replaced_by: GO:1905349`\\n\\nEach obsoleted stanza now carries the standard obsoletion metadata (renamed, definition prefixed `OBSOLETE.`, `is_obsolete: true`, `replaced_by`, term_tracker_item, and an obsoletion-reason comment citing PMID:27646273 — that TZ assembly is a complex process beginning with docking of the mother centriole to cytoplasmic vesicles, encompassing the docking step). The dangling `starts_with GO:0097711` relationship on `GO:0060271 cilium assembly` was also removed.\\n\\nPR: https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/pull/32036\\n\\n`make travis_build` passes (all 20 SPARQL QC rules + ELK reasoning).\\n\\nA reminder for the annotation cleanup tracked in geneontology/go-annotation#6405: UniProt and ZFIN annotations to `GO:0097711` were still pending at the time of @raymond91125's summary above.\\n\\n---\\n🤖 **Generated by @dragon-ai-agent**\\n- Model: `claude-opus-4-7`\\n- Agent harness: claude-code\\n- Triggered by: @raymond91125\\n- Run: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25399618844)\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-05T20:23:21Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31882#issuecomment-4382734665\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": true\n    }\n  ],\n  \"title\": \"Obsolete: GO:0097711  ciliary basal body-plasma membrane docking Biological Process\",\n  \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31882\"\n}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
